  .about-me
    .icon
      %i.fa.fa-hand-spock-o
    .about-me-title About
    .my-info
      .handsome

      .about-me-info

        .speech
          .about-me-text
            My name is German and I'm a Software Developer from Miami but currently living in the greatest city in the world, New York City! I am a hard worker with a passion for Software Development and Traveling.
            %br
            %br
            I love problem solving, exploring NYC, creating memories with friends, and pushing my body to its limits. Feel free to explore my projects and reach out! I'm always eager to make new friends, and tackle new challenges.
