          .emoji
            = image_tag "emoji.png"
            .icon-title Software Developer
            .icon-text I love to learn about new technologies, enjoy analyzing code, and building awesome apps that can make a difference
          .globe
            = image_tag "globe.png"
            .icon-title World Traveler
            .icon-text I've traveled to numerous different countries around the globe and love immersing myself in different cultures
          .spartan
            = image_tag "running.png"
            .icon-title Competitor
            .icon-text I've participated in numerous Spartan Races throughout the country and am always looking to challenge myself


